<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Eid Mubarak!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #FFFFFF; /* White background */
            color: #4E4E4E; /* Soft gray text */
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #1C92FB; /* Vibrant blue for headings */
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #1C92FB; /* Gold button */
            color: #FFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0B6DBF; /* Dark gold on hover */
        }
        .payment-details {
            display: none;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        input[type="text"] {
            padding: 10px;
            width: 80%;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .toast {
            visibility: hidden;
            min-width: 250px;
            background-color: #ff4444; /* Red background */
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 16px;
            position: fixed;
            z-index: 1;
            bottom: 30px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }
        .toast.show {
            visibility: visible;
            animation: fadein 0.5s, fadeout 0.5s 2.5s;
        }
        @keyframes fadein {
            from { bottom: 0; opacity: 0; }
            to { bottom: 30px; opacity: 1; }
        }
        @keyframes fadeout {
            from { bottom: 30px; opacity: 1; }
            to { bottom: 0; opacity: 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Eid al-Fitr: A Time for Gratitude</h1>
<p>As we bid farewell to Ramadan, letâ€™s carry its lessons of patience, gratitude, and compassion into the rest of the year. Eid Mubarak! <br>
<br><br><br><br>Your well-wisher<br>MUKTADIR</p>
    <button onclick="showPaymentDetails()" class="button">Get Salami</button>
    <div id="paymentDetails" class="payment-details">
        <p>Enter your Bkash/Nagad account number:</p>
        <input type="text" id="accountNumber" placeholder="01XXXXXXXXX" maxlength="11">
        <br>
        <button onclick="validateAccount()" class="button">Submit</button>
    </div>

    <!-- Toast Message -->
    <div id="toast" class="toast">Please enter a valid Bkash/Nagad account number (11 digits, starting with 01).</div>

    <script>
        function showPaymentDetails() {
            document.getElementById("paymentDetails").style.display = "block";
        }

        function validateAccount() {
            const accountNumber = document.getElementById("accountNumber").value;

            // Check if account number starts with 01 and is 11 digits long
            if (accountNumber.startsWith("01") && accountNumber.length === 11) {
                document.getElementById("bankDetails").style.display = "block";
            } else {
                showToast();
            }
        }

        function showToast() {
            const toast = document.getElementById("toast");
            toast.classList.add("show");
            setTimeout(() => {
                toast.classList.remove("show");
            }, 3000);
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
